          "scenario": "IT Job Lead Hi, I wanted to share a potential opportunity that may be a good fit for you. Position: IT Internal Operations Administrator Company: Siemens Location: Charlotte, TN This role focuses on providing IT support across a worksite, serving as a first point of contact for technical issues. Responsibilities include setting up and maintaining computers and devices, troubleshooting hardware and software problems, installing systems, and supporting employees with onboarding/offboarding IT needs. You would also help ensure network security, manage equipment, and assist with upgrades and new technology rollouts. It ’ s a hands-on IT support position that blends help desk functions with equipment maintenance and coordination with internal teams and vendors. If this sounds like something you ’ d be interested in, go ahead and apply using the link provided in your job portal. Let me know if you ’ d like help tailoring your resume or preparing for the role. — Mario McMichael Veteran Outreach Specialist IT Internal Operations Administrator Siemens Charlotte-TN Sincerely, Mario McMichael Veteran Outreach Specialist TDLWD (T): 615-532-7289 mario.mcmichael@tn.gov American Job Center - Clarksville * 523 Madison Street Suite B Clarksville, TN 37040 Phone: 931-648-5530 Extension: Days/Hours of operation: Monday- Friday 8:00 A.M.- 4:30 P.M. Northernmiddle.mailbox 1 @tn.gov Map Address Counties Served: Montgomery",
